     C* @INZ:INITIALIZE WORK AREA
     C***********************************************************
     C           @INZ      BEGSR
     C*
     C                     MOVE '0'       WKDSP   1
     C                     MOVE *ALL'0'   WKBLAK 10
     C                     Z-ADD1         BIN
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     W1RRN   40
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     G       40
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     Q       40
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     W#LAB   30
     C*
